## What belongs here

A product spec records the user story, acceptance criteria, and design decisions for a feature before implementation begins. Write one when:
- The feature affects the user experience in a non-trivial way.
- Multiple implementation approaches exist and the choice has UX implications.
- Stakeholder sign-off is required before building.

